kanban-simulator

Workflow simulator with specific configurations for a typical software development scenario.

To execute, run:

   $ ruby code/app/kanban_simulator.rb <number of stories to create>

for example, to create a backlog of 20 stories, 

   $ ruby code/app/kanban_simulator.rb 20

You can configure the simulation by editing the configuration file:
   $ $EDITOR code/app/simulation_config.txt
